 justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qua 4 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/bang-xep-hang-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018</span></span> v\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng (1-0) v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC (3-0).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du khoi dau tot nhung Than Quang Ninh khong duoc danh gia la nha vo dich V-League 2018 tiem nang.\" title=\"D\u00f9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/qn-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>D\u00f9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018, c\u1ef1u HLV B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n B\u00ecnh S\u1ef1 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean TTVN: &quot;&ldquo;D\u00f9 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9t m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. H\u1ecd v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n h\u01a1n ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y theo t\u00f4i nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh d\u00f9 \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u, tr\u00f4ng th\u1ebf th\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng d\u00f9 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n d\u00e0i, khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0o phom, h\u1ecd t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c th\u00ec r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Theo t\u00f4i Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong Top 5&quot;.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a hay HAGL d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs HAGL\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/17/ai-la-nha-vo-dich-vleague-2018-trong-mat-chuyen-gia-viet.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League 2018 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 d\u00e0y, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam t\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-chi-ra-van-de-cua-flc-thanh-hoa-sau-tran-gap-slna-168-183324.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Marian Mihail</span> \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n trong m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n HAGL ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 e ng\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd sau ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 ba \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V-League l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9. M\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby v\u00e0o 19h00 (5/4).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-tran-dai-chien-u23-cua-ha-noi-vs-hagl-168-183452.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/19/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-tran-dai-chien-u23-cua-ha-noi-vs-hagl.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-du-doan-tran-dai-chien-u23-cua-ha-noi-vs-hagl-168-183452.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn U23 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xung quanh tr\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs HAGL v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i 5/4 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"779","checkdouble":"183471"},{"date":"16:54 03/04","title":"CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u0129nh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/thanh-hoa-bat-ngo-linh-an-phat-cua-ldbd-chau-a.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{c